{"tid":1354611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圍村村口細易守難攻 衝頭者必需終極勇武","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:45:21.000Z","uid":115660,"like":25,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d2852310db0c7191cfb33f42aca037ccaa8eb7e9","tid":1354611,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"只要衝到入去 就係埋身戰<br />\n我地人多能盡量發揮人海優勢<br />\n<br />\n但衝唔到入去 村口互屌其實意義不大<br />\n<br />\n請問有無肯衝頭又以一當百既死士"},{"pid":"e4bc5091d10742cd6bc425ce82964f49910ea4be","tid":1354611,"uid":17354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"901e22f7eccfbd4ccb0e6db45d33e685b44ec962","tid":1354611,"uid":48544,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"[727光復元朗] 727元朗反黑反恐行動部署提議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354479</a><br />\n<br />\n可以睇下我嘅提議～<br />\n<br />\n727光復元朗 (副題：元朗反黑反恐行動) <br />\n口號：肅清鄉黑，除暴安良 <br />\n目的：以武力震懾元朗鄉黑勢力，保障元朗社區安全。 <br />\n<br />\n727香港人嘅主要目標有 <br />\n1. 針對鄉黑黃賭毒勢力經濟進行破壞 (首要目標：黃色經濟) <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好唔記得除咗元朗有黑社會之外。 <br />\n元朗區同屯門公園一樣，有色情流鶯問題。 <br />\n掃鄉黑圍村個時，幫埋元朗區搞掂埋黃色問題。 <br />\n<br />\n建議： <br />\n進行141洗樓行動，對流鶯進行驅趕。 <br />\n為咗cut班鄉黑嘅收入 <br />\n<br />\n一樓一地址141個網有架啦。我睇下post唔post出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非都可以係一樓一門口貼下紙仔 <br />\n個人推介可以貼五十路林鄭av封面圖同鄭若驊大波圖係一樓一舊樓門口。 <br />\n<br />\n勇武手足可以注意睇下啲粉紅光管，啲門口cam可以點做。<br />\n<br />\n同埋call埋入境處舉報有人違反逗留條件，入境處都有執法嘅權力。 <br />\n<br />\n舉報違反入境條例罪行 <a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Finvestigation%2Fonlinereportoffence.htm&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=1774c1b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm</a><br />\n電話：入境事務處24小時舉報熱線： (852) 2824 1551 (舉報後獲提供一個檔案編號) <br />\n<br />\n人地已經ready <br />\n［遍地開花］年輕紀律部隊要爬山 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n麻雀館大家睇下可以點搞，我唔熟<br />\n<br />\n地形分析：<br />\n【光復元朗】作為一個元朗居民我有啲野想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351965</a><br />\n我係一個由細到大都係圍村長大嘅港女，我有講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354569/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354569/page/1</a><br />\n想黎元朗搵好野食既朋友請入，為你介紹交通工具<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354599</a>"},{"pid":"f4b1c2515e4580192eb0c35261f5e29f8d44655f","tid":1354611,"uid":39855,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"其實冇須入村打巷戰，輸地型。"},{"pid":"41d9c3c9a7b241271b7cfbeb6cb229480f892913","tid":1354611,"uid":111955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"大家full gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f73b4cb592a4b92180ca3b3adf8f40b762bc3f4","tid":1354611,"uid":131696,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:29:59.000Z","msg":"真心 衝村同落單無咩分別<br />\n猛虎不及地頭蟲<br />\n唔熟路都算 仲要易俾白衫突襲<br />\n村口附近最穩陣"},{"pid":"7bcc3769937662200bbd0055ec418d40ae2a4fe9","tid":1354611,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6877e9f2c5424f7b6db5384e0a093c18ea8fa559","tid":1354611,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4b1c2515e4580192eb0c35261f5e29f8d44655f","tid":1354611,"uid":39855,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"其實冇須入村打巷戰，輸地型。"},"citedBy":2,