村口但唔好入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"圍村亂水電可行<br />\n<br />\n但作用不大<br />\n星期日個個會走<br />\n<br />\n同埋咪撚講咩入黑就走<br />\n驚佢老母最怕佢唔出黎"},{"pid":"ec6de2d7e372ba519420d3bec17e48a3266fcc84","tid":1354611,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:38:52.000Z","msg":"智取不可力敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7137c3bf79118f7cb31c9d593f2a3bdf3bef758d","tid":1354611,"uid":147345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"冇乜必要入村，而且唔好主動出手"},{"pid":"001fa486324976dac67c43ffc0a901d7732cc377","tid":1354611,"uid":205684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"入村我地一定冇晒地型優勢，真係要入就要太陽落山前。圍村人面好多間Kan位一般外人係唔會知。"},{"pid":"6bde81a24b5e99bb806230d9d064a77a472a7a79","tid":1354611,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:49:33.000Z","msg":"衝?<br />\n<br />\n唔係斷水斷電咩？ 好亂呀！"},{"pid":"c5fe766eb03032abb983c5115a3344bbad613a5c","tid":1354611,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e18e7c58fe8a6867fc66869e9a2dd7ea1bac6bd","tid":1354611,"uid":203774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"入去教仔姐 唔係虐兒就得"},{"pid":"4396c8f2449480158dbd5f209a4fb03eaf3eda2b","tid":1354611,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5fe766eb03032abb983c5115a3344bbad613a5c","tid":1354611,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45192059fd1a7dea8f96780861021cde2bf4